  "3219580": {
    "name": "茜塔和世界线悖论",
    "steam_appid": 3219580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >茜塔是一个碰到墙就会左转的小女孩，在快要沉没的世界中她捡到了能“分裂自己的概率”的叉子，从此一切就不一样了!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/cef654da6c37e3b391e022a5651b1615.poster.avif?t=1772477144\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/cef654da6c37e3b391e022a5651b1615.webm?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/cef654da6c37e3b391e022a5651b1615.mp4?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个关于分裂的游戏，从你自己到箱子，再到整个宇宙，和比宇宙更广阔的、由世界线交织而成的……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/45cb66d8e45eb1a404df571f45786523.poster.avif?t=1772477144\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/45cb66d8e45eb1a404df571f45786523.webm?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/45cb66d8e45eb1a404df571f45786523.mp4?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含六个主要的章节，每个章节都会揭露出至少一个已经存在于游戏第一章基础机制下的隐藏真相，所有的进阶机制和平行悖论从一开始就存在，只是你还没有发现它们！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对现代物理学的一种抽象演绎，揭秘包括平行宇宙的产生及运作方式、量子叠加和纠缠在内的各种规律</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/097d242b353646e67d4970ca7b5b31c6.poster.avif?t=1772477144\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/097d242b353646e67d4970ca7b5b31c6.webm?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/097d242b353646e67d4970ca7b5b31c6.mp4?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含240多个手工设计的谜题，以及使用改变“世界”的能力解决谜题之上的元谜题，获得闪亮的隐藏收集品</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/36bf2fdf8595b932ed5a91b4f4f6e617.poster.avif?t=1772477144\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/36bf2fdf8595b932ed5a91b4f4f6e617.webm?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/36bf2fdf8595b932ed5a91b4f4f6e617.mp4?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示系统和笔记：你可以随时查阅学习到的知识，或是在梦境中构思当前谜题的核心</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人放松的画面。如果你累了，可以坐下来休息!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/9359ac73127fe412616ec9cdd6952f5a.poster.avif?t=1772477144\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/9359ac73127fe412616ec9cdd6952f5a.webm?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/9359ac73127fe412616ec9cdd6952f5a.mp4?t=1772477144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点点添加愿望单</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ群：764710729</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras/270346b7a1be9e26ebfcc50bf5b75a27.avif?t=1772477144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219580/extras_big/270346b7a1be9e26ebfcc50bf5b75a27.avif?t=1772477144 width=800 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
